{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhlwqdissiw0","created":1775461944940,"text":"电饭煲-STM32F103C8T6"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrsivrh8140","created":1776059433034,"text":"功能","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgypb5a7u4g0","created":1773105124772,"text":"低糖饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0n30xio3k0","created":1773301966077,"text":"煮饭--PC15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃时，经PA5脚反馈后，PC15引脚高电平持续4min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0omz3i7gg0","created":1773306350479,"text":"焖饭--PC15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--27次，时长18min\n当NTC检测103℃，经P9脚反馈，PC15引脚低电平--继电器断开停止加热","layout":null,"priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0orzmnduo0","created":1773306743457,"text":"保温：65-70℃\nNTC检测温度低于65℃时，PC15引脚高电平10s，低电平20s--间歇加热\n高于70℃时，PC15引脚低电平--停止加热\n循环","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb63g16w0","created":1773105126539,"text":"柴火饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kitrnm600","created":1773802540765,"text":"预热--PC15高电平15s，低电平25s--时长2min；\nPC15引脚高电平10s，低电平30s；\n当NTC检测60℃，经P9脚反馈，PC15引脚高电平--持续加热","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kmzk0hso0","created":1773802866821,"text":"煮沸--当NTC检测100℃，经P9脚反馈，PC15引脚高电平20s，低电平20s；","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5ko9blmso0","created":1773802966444,"text":"出锅巴--当NTC检测102℃，经PA5反馈，PC15引脚高电平25s，低电平15s--开关2次；\nPC15引脚高电平32s，低电平8s--循环\n当NTC检测140℃，PC15引脚低电平12min（倒计时）","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5kusi71xs0","created":1773803478387,"text":"保温","priority":4,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb6hc6x40","created":1773105127379,"text":"杂粮饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5j5ij90pc0","created":1773798676469,"text":"煮饭--PC15引脚高电平--继电器启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，经P9脚反馈，PC15引脚高电平32s，低电平8s\n循环","priority":1,"expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh5j6fjbwc80","created":1773798748307,"text":"焖饭：\n当NTC检测103℃，PC15引脚高电平13s，低电平280s；\nPC15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s；高电平32s，低电平8s；\n高电平15s，低电平2